
IMAPAccount gmail-dagnachew
Host imap.gmail.com
User dagnachewa@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d /home/dagnachew/mailpass.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersion TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-dagnachew-remote
Account gmail-dagnachew

MaildirStore gmail-dagnachew-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail-dagnachew
Master :gmail-dagnachew-remote:
Slave :gmail-dagnachew-local:
# Exclude everything under the internal [Gmail] folder, except the interesting folders
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Sent-mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync All
